      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……そこに？\n本当なんですか？　冗談じゃなく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s next to me?\nAre you telling the truth? You’re not joking?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.633333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 14.200000000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "見えてないか。まあ、それはそうよね\n今までだって見えてなかったんだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you can’t see me? Well‚ I shouldn’t be surprised.\nYou haven’t been able to see me all this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 21.500000000000004
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、本当に見えない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ you really can’t see her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.500000000000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 24.291428565979007
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい……ここですよね？\n………………見えません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t. She’s here‚ right?\nI can’t see her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.491428565979017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 31.8580952326457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私の心臓は麻奈さんのものなんでしょ？\nだったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But my heart used to belong to her‚ right?\nWhich means…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.52476189931237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "関係が深いと見える、って訳じゃないらしい\n……でも、なぜか芽衣には見えてるんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which means it’s not just about having a strong connection.\nBut… for some reason‚ Mei can see her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.924761899312365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 46.49142856597903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
