      "text": "ちょっとした心の持ちようというか\nきっかけだと思うんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be a matter of perspective‚\nor just coincidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.547845753033975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、{user}くん\nどうして話したの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}.\nWhy did you tell her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.314512419700634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 57.18117908636731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "こうなった以上、隠しておくのは逆に良くないし\nそれなら、いっそ全部話そうって思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Given everything that’s happened‚ hiding it would have an adverse effect.\nSo I figured it would be best to get it all out in the open.",
        "id": ""
